Package: system-maid
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt6, policykit-1, e2fsprogs, coreutils, systemd, util-linux
Maintainer: A. Serhat KILIÇOĞLU <https://www.github.com/shampuan>
Description: Advanced System Cleaner for Debian based systems.
 This program is a system cleaner alternative to CCleaner or WiseCleaner.
 It aims to improve performance by safely making certain system settings 
 and protecting privacy by cleaning unnecessary waste.
